data.description: Imagine building a home from the ground up and including all the upgrades and extras that you have always dreamed of for your “Forever Home.”  From upgraded flooring, cabinets, countertops, lighting, faucets to windows and so much more AND have that home built on a scenic Lake view upgraded lot in a gated community.  That is what this lovely home was built for.  A “Forever Home” to build a lifetime of memories.  Sometimes plans change and that is what happened for the current owner.  They have an opportunity outside the state and want to explore that opportunity.  Although they absolutely love their home they are giving “You” the opportunity to make what they had hoped would be their forever home “Yours.”  And the Best part is you don’t have to wait for it to be Built!  It is already here with all the upgrades you can imagine.   This stunning, like-new home is absolutely beautiful and Move In Ready.  Situated in a prime location on an oversized Premium homesite, this property offers an abundance of desirable features and convenient amenities that will exceed your expectations.  The spacious layout encompasses four bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an oversized Great Room, Dining Area, Kitchen with an oversized Island, Upgraded Cabinets and Upgraded Appliances. It showcases modern finishes and many upgraded features that will delight any aspiring chef. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or preparing a meal, this kitchen will effortlessly cater to your culinary needs. The large Great room is a welcoming space, ideal for relaxing and spending quality time with friends or family.  It’s open design allows for seamless entertaining, making it the perfect gathering spot for memorable moments. Beautiful Upgraded Vinyl Plank Flooring throughout the Great Room and Kitchen area gives the area a Classic and Comfortable look and feel.  The Primary Suite Bathroom has floor to ceiling upgraded tiles in the large Shower, Garden Tub and Dual Vanities. The covered lanai provides the perfect vantage point to enjoy picturesque views of the tranquil pond and the oversized backyard. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting barbecues with this idyllic backdrop. Located in the Beautiful Serenoa Gated Community of Clermont, it includes an array of amazing amenities, including a beautiful resort style pool where you can cool off during hot summer days, a Splash Pad, a well-equipped Fitness Center, a Playground, Dog Park and much more. The possibilities for recreation and relaxation are endless. This Beautiful home is close to top-rated schools, shopping, nearby Attractions, Restaurants, all conveniently located. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a magnificent home that offers the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, numerous upgrades and amenities. Take advantage of this wonderful opportunity to make this your next home.  Make your dream a reality and schedule a viewing today.  Cash, FHA, VA, Conventional Financing.   No "Subject To" offers will be considered.
